Naina Devi Temple: Nainital Ki Aatma
23 April 2026

Nainital ka naam sunte hi do cheezein yaad aati hain - Naini Jheel aur Naina Devi Temple. Ye mandir sirf pathar aur moorti nahi hai, ye Nainital ki aatma hai. Har Nainital wale ke dil me Maa Naina Devi basti hain.

Itihaas Ka Panna: Kehte hain jab Bhagwan Shiv, Mata Sati ka shareer lekar tandav kar rahe the, to Bhagwan Vishnu ne Sudarshan Chakra se Sati ke shareer ke 51 tukde kar diye. Jahan-jahan ye tukde gire, wahan Shakti Peeth ban gaye. Nainital me Maa Sati ke Nain yaani aankhein giri thi. Isliye is jagah ka naam Nainital pada aur yahan Naina Devi ka mandir bana.

Mandir Ka Mahol: Subah 4 baje ki pehli ghanti ke saath hi poore Nainital me ek alag si urja aa jati hai. Thandi hawa, jheel ka pani aur mandir se aati aarti ki awaz - aadmi ka mann shuddh ho jata hai. Navratri ke dino me to yahan itni bheed hoti hai ki pair rakhne ki jagah nahi milti. Phir bhi Maa ke darbar me sabko shanti milti hai.

Mera Anubhav: Bachpan se jab bhi school me exam hote the, ya ghar me koi pareshaani aati thi, hum sabse pehle Naina Devi darshan ko jaate the. Maa ke saamne matha tek kar aisa lagta tha jaise saari chinta Maa ne le li ho. Aaj bhi jab mann bechain hota hai, jheel ke kinare baith kar mandir ko dekhta hu. Lagta hai Maa keh rahi hain - "Beta, dar mat. Main hu na."

Naini Jheel Aur Mandir Ka Rishta: Kehte hain Naini Jheel Maa Naina Devi ki aankhon ka prateek hai. Jheel ka paani jitna shaant aur gehra hai, Maa ki mamta bhi utni hi gehari hai. Mandir ke darshan ke baad jheel me boat ki sawari karna har bhakt ka niyam hai. Jaise Maa ne apni god me bitha kar jheel ki sair kara di ho.

Agar tum kabhi Nainital aao, to hotel aur Mall Road se pehle Naina Devi Temple zaroor jana. Yahan photo khichwane mat aana. Aankh band karke 2 minute Maa ke saath baithna. Jo shanti tumhe yahan milegi, woh Switzerland me bhi nahi milegi.

Jai Maa Naina Devi 🙏

